==Ancient Greek==
===Verb===
'''ἔρχομαι'''
# [[come]], [[go]]
===Usage Notes===
Ἔρχομαι is a deponent verb, and thus never takes an active form, only middle or passive.  See Wikipedia's article on [[w:Deponent verb|deponency]].
